	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "purchase-order-apis-collection",
		"name": "Purchase Order Integration APIs",
		"description": "Complete collection for testing MuleSoft Purchase Order Integration APIs\n\n## Architecture\n- **System APIs**: Flipkart System API (port 8081), Amazon System API (port 8082)\n- **Process API**: Purchase Order Process API (port 8083) - Reusable orchestration layer\n- **Experience API**: Purchase Order Experience API (port 8084) - Simplified interface for Flipkart to IBM\n\n## Use Cases\n1. **Flipkart → IBM**: Three-layer architecture (System → Process → Experience)\n2. **Amazon → HP**: Two-layer architecture (System → Process)\n\n## Test Order\n1. Test System APIs individually\n2. Test Process API transformations\n3. Test Experience API (Flipkart to IBM only)\n4. Verify end-to-end integration flows",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
